### List all posts (返回 data 包装的数据和 total)
GET http://localhost:3000/posts

### Search posts by title (按标题搜索)
GET http://localhost:3000/posts?_q=Hello

### Get single post (返回 data 包装的单个对象)
GET http://localhost:3000/posts/1

### Pagination with _page and _per_page (分页：第1页，每页2条)
GET http://localhost:3000/posts?_page=1&_per_page=2

### Pagination with _page and _limit (分页：第2页，每页2条)
GET http://localhost:3000/posts?_page=2&_limit=2

### Pagination with _start and _limit (分页：从索引1开始，取2条)
GET http://localhost:3000/posts?_start=1&_limit=2

### Create post (创建新文章)
POST http://localhost:3000/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hello, world!",
  "content": "This is my first post."
}

### Update post (更新文章)
PUT http://localhost:3000/posts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hello, world!",
  "content": "This is my first post. (updated)"
}

### Delete post (删除文章)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/posts/1

### Comments - List all (评论列表)
GET http://localhost:3000/comments

### Comments - Search by text (按文本搜索评论)
GET http://localhost:3000/comments?_q=comment

### Comments - Pagination (评论分页)
GET http://localhost:3000/comments?_page=1&_per_page=1